  - actorId: 0
    message: I have come to answer your riddle.
  - actorId: 1
    message: Then speak your name mortal
  - actorId: 1
    message: Let it be written in dust if you fail
  - actorId: 0
    message: kael
  - actorId: 0
    message: ' I am ready'
  - actorId: 1
    message: Then listen well, for I shall not repeat it
  - actorId: 1
    message: "\u7136\u53EF\u4EE5\uFF01\u4EE5\u4E0B\u662F\u9053\u9AD8\u5EA6\u7B97\u673A\u79D1\u5B66\u7684\u4E2D\u6587\u7FFB\uFF0C\u5305\u62EC\u4E00\u4E2A\u6B63\u786E\u7B54:"
  - actorId: 1
    message: Correct. Your mind is sharp, though your flesh is soft.
  - actorId: 0
    message: So... where is the papyrus?
  - actorId: 1
    message: I no longer guard it. I passed it to another... one not bound by riddles
  - actorId: 1
    message: 'A creature who cannot speak, but remembers everything '
  - actorId: 1
    message: You will find him in the library. Bound in a cage of runes and dust
  - actorId: 1
    message: To give you the papyrus you must give him the four memory pieces
  - actorId: 1
    message: 1.The Blue, Red and the Green Potions
  - actorId: 1
    message: And last the Book of knowledge
  - actorId: 1
    message: Now leave
  actors:
  - name: Kael
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 553556d207fc74b4f85fada0de3521fa, type: 3}
  - name: Skeleton
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0dd0b92af069dcd468c50da879d10216, type: 3}
  choiceManager: {fileID: 1733036932}
  InteractButton: {fileID: 606178382}
  backgroundBox: {fileID: 995158703}
