    message: "Yeah. Heard there is something valuable inside\u2014some kind of ancient
      papyrus?"
  - actorId: 1
    message: The Forbidden Papyrus. Lotta folks died chasing it There is a crew of
      treasure hunters inside already  They will kill anyone who stands between them
      and that scroll
  - actorId: 0
    message: What makes this papyrus so special?
  - actorId: 1
    message: It is guarded. Word is, there is a skeletal guardian that asks a riddle.
      One wrong answer, and you are a corpse on the floor.
  - actorId: 0
    message: And someone knows the answer?
  - actorId: 1
    message: I do not know for sure, but I have heard whispers. Some say there is
      a wizard deep in the dungeon who is been studying the papyrus.
  - actorId: 1
    message: If anyone knows the answer, it is probably him. Or maybe it is just
      a story to give desperate fools false hope.
  - actorId: 0
    message: Guess I will have to find out for myself.
  - actorId: 1
    message: Good luck. You will need it.
  actors:
  - name: Kael
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 553556d207fc74b4f85fada0de3521fa, type: 3}
  - name: Alex
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c9ec9e987a51ca44686010de5e66997e, type: 3}
  InteractButton: {fileID: 606178382}
  backgroundBox: {fileID: 995158703}
